::Rex::

Rex shakes his head, still frowning. Battera seemed sincere, but sincerity 
could be easily faked. As well as hysterics.

"No, only Predacons torture and kill like that," he says, his prejudiced 
views getting past him, "Its really up to the Maximal commander, I just don't 
think that peace between Maximals and Predacons would be successful."
